Heat the olive oil in a casserole dish or large saucepan. Add the sausages and cook until browned on all sides.Add the onion and fry for 3-4 minutes. Add the garlic and fry for a further minute.Add the red wine, tomato pur√©e, ketchup and beef stock and simmer for 8-10 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened and the sausages are completely cooked through.To serve, pour into a serving bowl and scatter with the chopped herbs.